high_descs: Go around the fridge and walk to the far wall. Face the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and then walk to the counter next to the stove.
Cut the lettuce with the knife.
Set the knife down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn around and walk toward the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Go to the fridge with the lettuce.
Put the lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce from the counter into the fridge after it is cut and washed.

high_descs: Turn right, go across the room, turn right and head toward the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter with the lettuce on it.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Put the knife on the spoon on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed slice of lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: TO wash a lettuce slice and place it in the fridge.
